### Description

Query job template details within the specified resource scope (business or business set) by job template ID, including global variables and all steps (including disabled steps).

Prerequisites: the target job template must exist; the caller must have permission to view the template in the resource scope.

### Request Parameters

#### Query Parameters

| Field             | Type   | Required | Description |
|-------------------|--------|----------|-------------|
| bk_scope_type     | string | Yes      | Resource scope type. Optional values: `biz` (business), `biz_set` (business set) |
| bk_scope_id       | string | Yes      | Resource scope ID, must match `bk_scope_type` |
| id                | long   | Yes      | Job template ID, must be greater than 0 and the template must exist |

### Request Example

- GET

```json
/api/v4/get_job_template_detail?bk_scope_type=biz&bk_scope_id=2&id=1000
```

