### Response Parameter Description

{% include '_generic_v4_response.md.j2' %}

#### data

| Field              | Type   | Always Present | Description |
|--------------------|--------|----------------|-------------|
| bk_scope_type      | string | Yes            | Resource scope type. Optional values: `biz` (business), `biz_set` (business set) |
| bk_scope_id        | string | Yes            | Resource scope ID |
| id                 | long   | Yes            | Job template ID |
| name               | string | Yes            | Job template name |
| description        | string | Yes            | Job template description; empty string if none |
| creator            | string | Yes            | Creator |
| create_time        | long   | Yes            | Create time, Unix timestamp in milliseconds |
| last_modify_user   | string | Yes            | Last modifier |
| last_modify_time   | long   | Yes            | Last modify time, Unix timestamp in milliseconds |
| global_var_list    | array  | Yes            | Global variable list; empty array if none |
| step_list          | array  | Yes            | Step list including all template steps (including disabled); empty array if none |

##### global_var_list[] element

| Field        | Type   | Always Present | Description |
|--------------|--------|----------------|-------------|
| name         | string | Yes            | Global variable name |
| type         | int    | Yes            | Variable type. Optional values: `1` (string), `2` (namespace), `3` (execute target list), `4` (cipher), `5` (associative array), `6` (index array) |
| description  | string | Yes            | Variable description |
| required     | int    | Yes            | Required flag. Optional values: `1` (yes), `0` (no) |
| value        | string | No             | Variable value when `type` is `1`, `2`, `4`, `5`, or `6`; cipher type returns `******` |
| execute_target | object | No             | Execute target when `type` is `3` |

##### execute_target

{% include '_generic_v4_execute_target_without_container_resp.md.j2' %}

